        'apm-help-nav-item',
        'apm-help-img-caption',
        '\x20tab.\x20Dark\x20Classic\x20is\x20recommended\x20for\x20dark\x20mode\x20users.\x20Themes\x20apply\x20after\x20a\x20page\x20reload.\x20If\x20you\x20use\x20a\x20bookmark\x20with\x20a\x20theme\x20in\x20the\x20URL,\x20set\x20the\x20theme\x20here\x20instead\x20—\x20APM\x20Master\x20applies\x20it\x20everywhere\x20including\x20PTP\x20and\x20direct\x20WO\x20links.',
        'apm-help-section-title',
        'APM\x20Master\x20monitors\x20your\x20EAM\x20session\x20and\x20helps\x20you\x20recover\x20when\x20things\x20go\x20wrong.',
        '1px\x20solid\x20var(--apm-border,\x20#45535e)',
        'var(--apm-accent,\x20#3498db)',
        'APM\x20Master\x20keeps\x20track\x20of\x20your\x20place\x20as\x20you\x20work\x20—\x20the\x20screen\x20you\x27re\x20on,\x20the\x20record\x20you\x20have\x20open,\x20your\x20search\x20filters,\x20and\x20even\x20the\x20active\x20tab.\x20If\x20your\x20session\x20expires\x20or\x20the\x20page\x20reloads,\x20a\x20restore\x20prompt\x20slides\x20in\x20offering\x20to\x20take\x20you\x20right\x20back\x20where\x20you\x20were.',
        '380px',
        'apm-help-img-row',
        'apm-help-img\x20apm-help-img-sm',
        'Save\x20your\x20filter\x20combinations\x20as\x20named\x20profiles\x20to\x20quickly\x20switch\x20between\x20different\x20views.',
        'Date\x20Override\x20enabled\x20—\x20the\x20profile\x20controls\x20its\x20own\x20target\x20week\x20and\x20day\x20selection.',
        '\x20OR\x20',
        'motor',
        'Toggle\x20this\x20on\x20to\x20give\x20the\x20profile\x20its\x20own\x20date\x20range.\x20When\x20enabled,\x20the\x20main\x20Forecast\x20date\x20picker\x20disappears\x20and\x20is\x20replaced\x20by\x20the\x20profile\x27s\x20own\x20target\x20week\x20and\x20day\x20selection\x20—\x20so\x20you\x20always\x20know\x20exactly\x20what\x20dates\x20the\x20profile\x20will\x20search.',
        'PM_and_Non_PM_Filter_toggle',
        'Clears\x20the\x20filter\x20and\x20shows\x20the\x20full\x20unfiltered\x20results.',
        'colorcode',
        'apm-help-img\x20apm-help-img-half',
        'Multi-Keyword:\x20',
        ')\x20to\x20match\x20any\x20of\x20them\x20with\x20one\x20rule.',
        'Create\x20templates\x20for\x20recurring\x20work\x20orders.\x20When\x20APM\x20detects\x20a\x20matching\x20WO,\x20a\x20teal\x20Auto\x20Fill\x20button\x20appears\x20on\x20the\x20record\x20toolbar.',
        'apm-help-img-row-caption',
        'Autofill\x20can\x20also\x20book\x20labor\x20hours\x20to\x20the\x20work\x20order\x20as\x20part\x20of\x20the\x20automated\x20process,\x20good\x20for\x20repetetive\x20work\x20orders\x20with\x20predictable\x20labor.',
        'Partial\x20Fill:\x20',
        'Auto\x20Fill\x20button\x20on\x20a\x20work\x20order',
        'The\x20teal\x20Auto\x20Fill\x20button\x20appears\x20contextually\x20on\x20matching\x20work\x20orders.',
        'apm-help-img',
        'Labor\x20Tally\x20—\x20dockable\x20widget\x20showing\x20your\x20hours\x20at\x20a\x20glance.',
        'Correction\x20Mode:\x20',
        'Add\x20other\x20employee\x20IDs\x20in\x20the\x20Labor\x20Tally\x20to\x20view\x20their\x20hours.\x20Select\x20from\x20the\x20dropdown\x20to\x20switch\x20between\x20employees.\x20Must\x20have\x20APM\x20permissions\x20to\x20view\x20other\x20Employees.',
        'Switch\x20to\x20\x22Grid\x20Columns\x22\x20mode\x20to\x20drag\x20columns\x20into\x20your\x20preferred\x20order.',
        'Resize\x20Columns:\x20',
        '\x20to\x20load\x20today\x27s\x20work\x20orders.\x20Press\x20',
        'Work\x20order\x20numbers\x20in\x20the\x20grid\x20are\x20automatically\x20hyperlinked.\x20Click\x20to\x20open\x20in\x20EAM.\x20Use\x20the\x20clipboard\x20icon\x20to\x20copy\x20—\x20pastes\x20as\x20a\x20clickable\x20link\x20in\x20Slack,\x20Teams,\x20and\x20email.',
        '14px',
        '20px',
